撚慘！<br />\n我一定要強烈譴責你哋呢一班暴徒！"},{"pid":"e2cb51764cb68a2c52f6ede75ac9da980818b557","tid":1409171,"uid":242132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:02:07.000Z","msg":"警察宿舍超平租有無得煲大佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1409970/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1409970/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"daa9f23348b1968accc122d94c26de2873c22261","tid":1409171,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0ddbb3472bcc6f8fb0e94b91feb6c3c16714809","tid":1409171,"uid":171302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dd29c018afbc440c501468e0adfc339eedb9b10c","tid":1409171,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:35:57.000Z","msg":"唔係我驚你地全家都會好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:38:51.000Z","msg":"你班後生仔玩乜都唔啱㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家千祈唔好打爆佢個火警鐘，嘈到成座住户就唔好啦！ 你知啦， 你哋喺下面搞搞震，佢哋最多閂窗， 咁就咩都聽唔到！<br />\n<br />\n但係打爆個火警鐘，咁樣就會全棟樓都聽到。仲要冇電梯，行幾十層樓梯落嚟喎。夜麻麻真係唔好咁樣搞人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好冇陰德囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有啊，突別係停車場啲火警鐘同埋灑水系統就最仆街。你班暴徒整爆個灑水系統，一陣射晒啲鹹水落停車場嗰度。你老味，入面啲幾十萬㗎！換轉你地班暴徒架車鹹水報銷左，你地點過意得去？<br />\n<br />\n屌你地班後生仔，我試過慢慢俾人三點俾人火警鐘誤嗚，第二日又要返工， 真係好撚慘！<br />\n我一定要強烈譴責你哋呢一班暴徒！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}